thread.title: Cardinals earn 15-point win over Bulldogs

author: Chaz Wright | sports@joplinglobe.com
title: Cardinals earn 15-point win over Bulldogs
text:
Close
Featured Cardinals earn 15-point win over Bulldogs By Chaz Wright | sports@joplinglobe.com Jan 23, 2025 Jan 23, 2025 1 min to read +1 +1
The Webb City High School girls basketball team earned a win Tuesday evening against old Central Ozark Conference foe Carl Junction High School, defeating them 62-47. The win is Webb City’s third straight and they improved to 9-5 on the year.
Carl Junction drops their second straight and falls to 5-7 on the season.
